Search Buttons Bar v1.2.1 (released 2016-08-01)
- Fix engine container's customization mode appearance.
- Fix engine icon max height in other toolbars.
Search Buttons Bar v1.2 (released 2016-07-03)
- Add overflow support for search buttons.
- Add a limit for the maximum width of search button.
- Fix scroll bar hiding the select buttons in the options dialog.
- Fix search buttons container over sizing.
- Fix bug with currentset persististing on Firefox.
- Fix bug with empty search engine icons.
- Fix search bar initialization on addon first run with defaultset.
- Fix search bar restoring on addon uninstall with defaultset.
Search Buttons Bar v1.1 (released 2016-06-06)
- Add basic options.
- Add option to select search buttons to show.
- Add icon for the addon.
- Fix issues with latest Firefox.
- Fix styling issue of search bar text field with Windows High Contrast theme.
- Fix search bar resizing splitters visibility.
- Fix open in new tab option.
- Fix removing of default search engines.
Search Buttons Bar v1.0 (released 2016-06-01)
- Initial working release.
